summary: Transcription model for Paul d'Estournelles de Constant French typewritten letters (1914-1924)
description: This model was trained on the dahncorpus dataset, using the NFC Unicode normalization. The dahncorpus dataset contains documents written in French by Paul d'Estournelles de Constant from 1914 to 1924. For more details on the dataset and the transcription guidelines, see https://github.com/HTR-United/dahncorpus. This dataset and model were created as part of the DAHN project. For more details on the project, see https://github.com/FloChiff/DAHNProject.
name: model_pec_9789_nfc.mlmodel
